          <p>The <%= link_to 'Pupil Progress Plan', '/pricing' %>, which year groups throughout primary schools follow, builds secure foundations and long term success in Maths, focusing on developing confidence, fluency and mastery.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 block-text-column">
        <article class="top-border-blue">
          <h3>How we teach for mastery</h3>
          <p>Many elements of Singapore Maths are incorporated to help pupils become fluent in the fundamentals of Maths, reason mathematically and apply their maths to problem solving. We strive in all situations to incorporate real world examples and adapt each lesson to a childâ€™s interest and needs.</p>
        </article>
