          <h3>Data drives continuous improvement</h3>
          <p>Each week we record thousands of hours of one-to-one online Maths tuition sessions for training and professional development purposes. This enables us to identify the teaching methods and factors that engender the best learning outcomes for pupils and continually improve our lessons, resources and pedagogy.</p>
        </article>
